Name: Landing Gear
Description: Includes Basic Structure which provides major support for the aircraft, while on the ground, such as Struts, Linkage,Bolts, Latches, Attachment Fittings, etc.

Name: Doors
Description: Includes Basic Framework and Structure such as Angles,Formers, Ribs, Stringers, Fittings, Intercostal Brackets, etc.

SecondaryCodes.Name: Primary Structure
SecondaryCodes.Description: Includes Primary Structure such as Frames, Bulkheads, Beams, Formers, Longerons, Stringers, Sills, Keel, etc.

SecondaryCodes.Name: Auxiliary Structure
SecondaryCodes.Description: Includes Secondary Structure such as Floors, Fixed Partitions, etc.

SecondaryCodes.Name: Plates/Skin
SecondaryCodes.Description: Includes Exterior Covering such as Skin, Access Covers,and Doublers.

SecondaryCodes.Name: Attach Fittings
SecondaryCodes.Description: Includes Seat Tracks and Fittings or Drag Angles on Fuselage for attachment of Doors, Wings, Stabilizers, L. Gear, Engine, and Pylons.

SecondaryCodes.Name: Primary Structure
SecondaryCodes.Description: Includes Primary Skeleton of Nacelle Pylon such as Frames,Bulkheads, Firewalls, Stringers, Keel, and Frames around openings.

SecondaryCodes.Name: Plates/Skin
SecondaryCodes.Description: Includes Exterior Covering such as Skin, Access Covers, and Doublers.

Name: Stabilizers
Description: Includes Basic Internal Structure such as Spars, Ribs, Stringers, Plates/Skin Access Covers, Tabs, and Support of Equipment within Stabilizer.

Name: Window
Description: Includes the Transparent Material and its Frame.

SecondaryCodes.Name: Wing Main Structure
SecondaryCodes.Description: Primary Skeleton – Includes Spars, Ribs, Upper and Lower Skin Panels, Attach Fittings, Stringers, Internal Fuel Tank Structure, Frames.

SecondaryCodes.Name: Trailing Edge Flaps
SecondaryCodes.Description: Includes Skins, Panel and Stiffener, Ribs, Fittings, Tracks.
